    <item>
      <title>由于避险基调抵消了中东风险，油价将每周下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储政策制定者的鹰派言论推动了更广泛的避险情绪，抵消了伊朗和以色列之间的中东紧张局势，油价今年首次连续一周下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:23:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度大规模选举拉开帷幕，莫迪押注第三任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近10亿印度人周五开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，权衡是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的混合政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金对中国教育公司违约表示不满</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/hedge-funds-cry-foul-over-chinese-education-firm-s-default</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家盈利的中国教育公司三月份对其可转换债券违约后，对冲基金和其他国际投资者发出了警报。]]></description>
